nFrom e66bfa3bac1e2f198e456513d0494b45e6d68699 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:55:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: always-visible directions link, star rating, enriched
 legal pages

1. Event details: 'Get directions' button now ALWAYS shows (uses
   coordinates when available, falls back to venue+city+region address
   search on Google Maps). Previously hidden when event had no coords.
2. Feedback page: replaced the rating <Select> dropdown with interactive
   clickable stars (hover + fill effect). Much better UX.
3. Legal enrichment: Terms of Service gains Intellectual Property,
   Limitation of Liability, Governing Law sections. Privacy Policy gains
   Data Retention, Your Rights, Cookies & Tracking, Children's Privacy.
   All content in EN + FR.
